name: Snakanake
description:
Tiny unfair game made in less than a day for Mini Jam 111, based on the limitation/theme "You Are Your Own Enemy"
It's missing a lot of features, mainly balance, particles, & general polish, but i'm happy to get it out this quickly

Palette is a subset of Sweetie 16
Music by Kevin MacLeod
Based on an idea by jumbletraveling
